These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
Nationality: canadian, thai, mexican, russian
Cigar: aristoff, old-henry, bongani, oliveros
1. Cigar:oliveros is on the left of Nationality:mexican##1
2. Nationality:canadian is on the left of Cigar:old-henry##1
3. Nationality:russian is in an odd position##4
4. Cigar:bongani is on the left or right of Cigar:oliveros##3
5. Nationality:canadian is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Nationality   | canadian | thai | russian | mexican |
| Cigar        | aristoff | old-henry   | oliveros | bongani    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
Flower: bellflower, balloon-flower, aconite, orchid
Color: lilac, brown, yellow, turquise
1. Flower:balloon-flower is on the left of Flower:orchid##1
2. Color:lilac is on the left of Color:yellow##1
3. Color:yellow is in an odd position##4
4. Color:lilac == Flower:bellflower##1
5. Color:brown is on the right of Color:yellow##1
6. Color:lilac == Flower:bellflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Flower   | aconite | bellflower  | balloon-flower  | orchid |
| Color   | turquise    | lilac | yellow | brown    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
Transport: scooter, tram, bike, skateboard
House: gothic-revival, townhouse, craftsman, tower
1. Transport:skateboard is on the left or right of House:tower##3
2. Transport:bike is in an even position##4
3. House:tower is on the left or right of Transport:tram##3
4. House:tower is on the right of House:craftsman##1
5. House:gothic-revival is in an odd position##4
6. Transport:tram is on the right of Transport:bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Transport          | skateboard | bike | tram    | scooter      |
| House   | craftsman        | tower     | gothic-revival | townhouse |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
House: futuristic, wooden, craftsman, ranch-style
Cigar: havana, alhambra, bongani, davidoff
1. House:wooden is between Cigar:havana and Cigar:davidoff##2
2. House:ranch-style is on the left of House:futuristic##1
3. Cigar:bongani is in an odd position##4
4. Cigar:alhambra is on the left of Cigar:davidoff##1
5. Cigar:alhambra is on the right of House:futuristic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| House         | ranch-style | futuristic | wooden | craftsman |
| Cigar   | bongani       | havana   | alhambra    | davidoff  |

