.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
Birthday: march, february, august, april
Flower: aconite, sunflower, lily, orchid
1. Birthday:august is on the right of Flower:orchid##1
2. Flower:sunflower == Birthday:april##1
3. Flower:lily is on the right of Birthday:march##1
4. Birthday:february is on the far left##1
5. Birthday:august is in an odd position##4
6. Flower:aconite is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Birthday   | february  | march    | august   | april       |
| Flower   | aconite | orchid | lily | sunflower |

