Flower: sunflower, aconite, daisy, begonia
1. Flower:aconite is in an even position##4
2. Food:carrot is on the right of Flower:aconite##1
3. Food:cabbage is in an odd position##4
4. Flower:sunflower is on the left of Food:cauliflower##1
5. Flower:daisy is on the left or right of Flower:sunflower##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |     4     |
| Food   | cabbage      | zucchini | carrot | cauliflower |
| Flower   | begonia | aconite     | sunflower  | daisy  |

