2. Game:poker is on the left of Game:billiard##1
3. Cigar:aristoff is on the left of Cigar:bluemaster##1
4. Game:monopoly == Cigar:vegafina##1
5. Cigar:aristoff is on the left or right of Game:billiard##3
6. Game:backgammon is on the right of Game:billiard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |     4     |
| Cigar   | vegafina | aristoff | bluemaster | dunhill    |
| Game     | monopoly | poker  | billiard     | backgammon |

