.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-8::.
Birthday: december, july, june, may
Movie-Genre: crime, disaster, musical, action
1. Movie-Genre:action is on the left or right of Birthday:july##3
2. Birthday:may is in an odd position##4
3. Movie-Genre:action is on the left or right of Birthday:may##3
4. Birthday:may is on the right of Movie-Genre:action##1
5. Birthday:december is between Birthday:may and Birthday:july##2
6. Movie-Genre:disaster is in an odd position##4
7. Movie-Genre:disaster is between Birthday:december and Movie-Genre:musical##2
8. Birthday:december is on the left or right of Birthday:july##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |     2      |    3    |        4        |
| Birthday   | july | december      | may | june |
| Movie-Genre   | crime  | action | disaster    | musical            |

