.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
City: hamburg, venice, liverpool, london
Cigar: bluemaster, old-henry, havana, chaman
1. City:hamburg == Cigar:chaman##1
2. Cigar:bluemaster is on the right of City:hamburg##1
3. Cigar:chaman is between Cigar:bluemaster and City:liverpool##2
4. City:hamburg is in an odd position##4
5. Cigar:chaman is on the left or right of Cigar:bluemaster##3
6. City:venice is on the left or right of Cigar:old-henry##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| City      | venice       | liverpool   | hamburg | london |
| Cigar   | havana | old-henry | chaman        | bluemaster    |

