.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-18::.
Birthday: august, may, june, december
City: boston, hamburg, miami, venice
1. City:hamburg is on the far left##1
2. Birthday:june is on the left or right of Birthday:august##3
3. Birthday:december is on the far left or far right##3
4. City:miami is on the left of City:venice##1
5. City:venice is on the right of Birthday:august##1
6. City:miami is in an even position##4
7. City:boston == Birthday:may##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Birthday   | december | august    | june       | may |
| City       | hamburg  | miami | venice | boston  |

