.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-20::.
Birthday: march, june, january, november
Movie-Genre: mystery, satire, western, thriller
1. Birthday:june is in an even position##4
2. Birthday:june is on the left or right of Movie-Genre:mystery##3
3. Movie-Genre:satire is between Birthday:march and Movie-Genre:mystery##2
4. Birthday:june is on the far left or far right##3
5. Movie-Genre:western is on the right of Birthday:november##1
6. Movie-Genre:western is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |    2    |         3          |    4    |
| Birthday         | march | january   | november | june |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller          | satire | mystery         | western  |

 